data.description: Four bedroom brick home, ready for a buyers touch. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout ready to be finished! Two bedrooms on the main floor and a full bathroom. Tons of living space! Large living room with tons of natural light , dining room and kitchen. Potential to create an open concept main floor. Upstairs find two well sized bedrooms and a second full bathroom. Finished basement with laundry room. Plenty of space to create a great game area. Great backyard, large driveway, and integral garage. Close to all Monroeville has to offer!
